query:
/*+  */ select l.l_shipmode,
sum(case when o.o_orderpriority = '1-URGENT' OR o.o_orderpriority = '2-HIGH' then 1 else 0 end) AS high_line_count,
sum(case when o.o_orderpriority <> '1-URGENT' AND o.o_orderpriority <> '2-HIGH' then 1 else 0 end) AS low_line_count
from lineitem AS l
inner join orders AS o
on o.o_orderkey = l.l_orderkey AND l.l_shipmode IN ('SHIP',
'RAIL') AND l.l_commitdate < l.l_receiptdate AND l.l_shipdate < l.l_commitdate AND l.l_receiptdate >= '1993-01-01'::date AND l.l_receiptdate < '1993-01-01'::date + '1'::interval(4) group by l.l_shipmode order by l.l_shipmode;
